unit triangle

A 3d Printable triangular unit that can be joined together to form various types of shapes , containers , etc , thats the idea. 
The units are made of light weight material and can be rearranged to make all sorts of required container shapes.. 
Its uses are many , including :
  -making containers to store things in and attach them to metallic part so that it won't float away in zero G.
  -can be used as solar sails.
  -can be used as solar panels on moon / mars roovers / or space vehicles.
  -It can even be used as armor for roovers in tough weathered climates like that of mars . 
  and many more things that can be imagined. 
The Triangles are joined together by magnets which are fitted at their vertices. 
